						               													<description>You&amp;rsquo;re volunteers at an adoption fair trying to find the best homes for your shelter&amp;rsquo;s puppies! You will present each puppy with a set of cards which represent a home you&amp;rsquo;ve found. Each home offers different amounts of Food, Love, or Room in varying combinations.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Goal: The player who offers the best home gets to keep a record of that adoption in their portfolio. Score points by collecting cards with matching ranks, suits, and breeds. The player with the most points wins!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How to Play: On your turn, you may draw two cards and allow your opponents to draw one. OR you may offer a set of cards to a puppy that is available from the center of the table or in front of another player. Your offer must meet certain minimum requirements noted by the puppy's tag. If taking a puppy from an opponent, you must offer a *better* set of cards, again based on the puppy's tag. If you begin your turn with a puppy in front of you, then add that card to your portfolio where it will be scored at the end of the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
